query:
SELECT p.id, s.name as service_name, c.name as country_name, p.apiId, p.smshubPrice, p.ourPrice
FROM prices p
JOIN services s ON p.serviceId = s.id
JOIN countries c ON p.countryId = c.id
WHERE s.name LIKE '%Outros%' AND p.apiId = 2
LIMIT 5;
